Author Amy Larkin discusses her 
book, "Environmental Debt: The Hidden Costs of a Changing 
Global Economy," in which she writes that every financial 
transaction has an environmental impact. Larkin talked with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on  Bloomberg Radio 's 
"Taking Stock" on June 25.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 15:45
 